        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/700/1*rqPCvf3mRrl9pGKW76wcTw.jpeg"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;"><strong>Image credit: Taken from google search, source was not mentioned. Let me know if it is your image and I can add the credit</strong></p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">In the image above H represents the output of the activation function.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">2. <strong>One to Many RNN</strong>: One to Many architecture refers to a situation where a RNN generates a series of output values based on a single input value. A prime example for using such an architecture will be a <strong>music generation</strong> task, where an input is a jounre or the first note.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
