        <div class="container"><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-9"><blockquote><p class="ff4">A bi-directional RNN consists of a forward and a backward recurrent neural network and final prediction is made combining the results of both the networks at any given time t, as can be seen in the image.</p></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
